Date: Fri, 11 Mar 2022 16:11:20 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 52/70] net: ethernet: renesas: rcar-taurus: Add virtual
 Ethernet driver over Taurus

This patch adds Para virtualized Ethernet driver.

Signed-off-by: Phong Hoang <phong.hoang.wz@renesas.com>
